     <li>Select <strong>Number</strong> as type.</li> 
     <li>Tap <strong>Create</strong>.</li> 
    </ol> <p>Repeat step 4 and 5 to create the following variables:</p> 
    <ul> 
     <li>Payments: Number type</li> 
     <li>Adjustments: Number type</li> 
     <li>Amountdue: Number type</li> 
     <li>Duedate: Date type</li> 
    </ul> </li> 
   <li><p>Create static text for the following fields using the right pane:</p> 
    <ul> 
     <li>Previous Balance</li> 
     <li>Payments</li> 
     <li>Adjustments</li> 
     <li>Charges current bill period</li> 
     <li>Amount Due</li> 
     <li>Due Date</li> 
     <li>Late payment charges after Due Date is $ 20</li> 
