   <li><p>Select the <strong>Data Model Objects</strong> tab, place the cursor next to the <strong>Charges current bill period</strong> field in the right pane, and double-click the <strong>bills</strong> &amp;gt; <strong>usagecharges</strong> property.</p> <img imageRotate="0" src="assets/bill_summary_static_variables.png" /></li> 
   <li><p>Click <strong>Save</strong> to create the Customer Details text document fragment.</p> </li> 
  </ol> 
  <h2>Step 4: Create Summary of charges text document fragment</h2> 
  <p>The Summary of charges document fragment includes the following fields:</p> 
